    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚与中国关系升温 但仍有“安全忧虑”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/australia-has-security-anxieties-with-china-even-as-ties-warm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总理理查德·马尔斯表示，尽管贸易关系已经稳定，但澳大利亚对与中国的关系仍存在“安全担忧”，并呼吁北京维护基于规则的全球秩序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/australia-has-security-anxieties-with-china-even-as-ties-warm</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 03:58:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
